FormHelper loses some data when label of optgroup is numeric from output html elements.

## Example case

```php
// controller
$tags = $this->Tag->find('list', ['fields' => ['id', 'name', 'category_id']]);
$this->set((compact('tags'));

// .ctp
$this->Form->input('tag_id');
```

## Example data in $tags

```
[
    '1' => [
        '1' => 'Foo',
        '2' => 'Bar',
    ],
    '2' => [
        '3' => 'Baz',
    ],
    '3' => [
        '4' => '2Foo',
        '5' => '2Bar',
    ],
];
```

`'4' => '2Foo'` or `'5' => '2Bar'` will be lost in this case.

